title: 09/06/21 DPS Hour 1
itunes:title: 09/06/21 DPS Hour 1
description:
Jonas Knox, Brady Quinn, and LaVar Arrington, in for Dan, react to Notre Dame beating Florida State in overtime on Sunday night and discuss Brian Kelly's controversial postgame comments. The guys dive into the biggest college football games of the weekend, including Penn State beating Wisconsin. One of the best moments of the year in sports took place on Sunday night. Plus, the Cowboys are in big trouble for Thursday night's season opener!
